I absolutely loved my visit to Bistro Claytopia! It’s the perfect blend of cozy dining and artistic fun. The atmosphere is charming—bright, welcoming, and full of whimsical details. While enjoying a delicious lunch ( their chicken lasagna was amazing!), I got to pick out a ceramic piece to paint as well! Go spend a cute summer day @bistroclaytopiakoramangala
